---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Career Transition | Veteran Support Services"
  description="Discover career transition services available to UK veterans through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme. Learn about job placement, training programmes, and educational support.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Career Transition Support for Veterans</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">The Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) is committed to supporting veterans in their transition to civilian careers. This page outlines the various career transition services and resources available to help you build a successful post-military career.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Career Counselling and Guidance</h2>
        <p>Our career counselling services include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>One-on-one sessions with career advisors</li>
          <li>Skills assessment and career matching</li>
          <li>Goal setting and career planning</li>
          <li>Guidance on translating military skills to civilian roles</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">CV Writing and Interview Skills</h2>
        <p>We offer practical support to help you secure civilian employment:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>CV writing workshops</li>
          <li>Interview preparation and mock interviews</li>
          <li>Personal branding and LinkedIn profile optimisation</li>
          <li>Networking skills development</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Job Placement Assistance</h2>
        <p>Our job placement services include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access to a database of veteran-friendly employers</li>
          <li>Job fairs and networking events</li>
          <li>Partnerships with recruitment agencies specialising in veteran placement</li>
          <li>Support for those interested in self-employment or entrepreneurship</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Vocational Training Programmes</h2>
        <p>We offer various training opportunities to enhance your skills:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Industry-specific certification courses</li>
          <li>Apprenticeship programmes</li>
          <li>IT and digital skills training</li>
          <li>Leadership and management courses</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Educational Support</h2>
        <p>For those pursuing further education, we provide:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Information on educational entitlements and funding</li>
          <li>Assistance with university and college applications</li>
          <li>Study skills workshops</li>
          <li>Mentoring programmes connecting veterans with academic advisors</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Related Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/support/mental-health" class="text-decoration-none">Mental Health Support</a></li>
              <li><a href="/financial/budgeting" class="text-decoration-none">Financial Planning</a></li>
              <li><a href="/support/housing" class="text-decoration-none">Housing Assistance</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Career Transition Workshop</h3>
            <p>Join our upcoming workshop on transitioning to civilian careers. Learn valuable skills and network with potential employers.</p>
            <a href="/career-workshop" class="btn btn-primary">Register Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
